        YOUTUBE DOWNLOADER PLUS - CHANGELOG v1.0.7
================================================================================

Release: Version 1.0.7 (Updated from Version 1.0.5)

Overview:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
YouTube Downloader Plus for Windows has been updated to version 1.0.7. This
release introduces several major new features, resolves critical bugs present
in previous versions, and delivers significant improvements to overall
stability and user experience.


================================================================================
NEW KEY FEATURES
================================================================================

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. VIDEO COMMENTS INTERFACE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

In version 1.0.5 and earlier, the video comments feature was non-functional.
With this update, the comments retrieval system has been completely rebuilt
and is now fully stable.

Key Highlights:
  - Fetch all available comments for any video, regardless of volume, even
    for videos with millions of comments.
  - Filter comments by "Recent" or "Popular," consistent with YouTube's
    native sorting options.
  - Search comments by author name or keyword.
  - Copy individual comments or export the entire comments list for
    convenient offline access.
  - The comments list displays each comment along with its author name,
    timestamp, and other relevant details.
  - When you select or navigate to a comment using the mouse or keyboard,
    the full comment text is displayed in a dedicated text box.
  - When you reach the end of the loaded comments list via keyboard or
    mouse navigation, the next batch of 100 comments is automatically
    fetched and appended.

How to Use:
  - Press CTRL+SHIFT+J, or navigate to the Video Options menu and open
    the Video Comments section while a video is playing.


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2. TRANSCRIPTS / SUBTITLES / CAPTIONS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

In version 1.0.5 and earlier, AI-generated transcriptions and YouTube's
official transcriptions were introduced as a demonstration. This version
delivers a significantly more advanced and fully functional transcript
retrieval system.

Key Highlights:
  - Retrieve both automatically generated and manually authored transcripts.
  - Support for all available transcript languages associated with a video.
  - All available languages are populated in a dropdown menu for easy
    selection (e.g., "Hindi - Automatically Generated").
  - Copy or export transcripts for convenient offline access and use.
  - This feature has been tested with the MrBeast YouTube channel, which
    offers transcripts in more than 20 languages.

How to Use:
  - Press CTRL+SHIFT+T, or navigate to the Video Options menu and open
    the Transcripts section.
  - Select the desired language from the dropdown menu.
  - Click "Load Transcripts" to retrieve and display the transcript.


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
3. FACEBOOK DOWNLOADER TOOL (DEMONSTRATION)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

As part of the ongoing goal to evolve this application into a cross-platform
media downloader, a Facebook video downloader has been introduced in version
1.0.7 as a demonstration feature.

Key Highlights:
  - Download videos directly from Facebook.
  - Option to download as MP3 audio.
  - Eliminates the need to search the internet for a trustworthy third-party
    downloading service.

How to Use:
  - Open the "More Tools" menu using the ALT key or ALT+M from the main
    interface.
  - Navigate to "Facebook Downloader" and open the tool.
  - Enter or paste the Facebook video link.
  - Check "Download as MP3 Audio" if an audio-only download is desired.
  - Click "Download and Save."


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
4. MEDIA PLAYER ENHANCEMENTS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Several new keyboard shortcuts and improvements have been added to the
built-in media player.

  a) Playback Speed Control:
     - Press "F" to increase the playback rate by 0.1x
       (e.g., from 1.1x to 1.2x).
     - Press "S" to decrease the playback rate by 0.1x.

  b) Total Duration Information:
     - Press "T" to retrieve and announce the total duration of the
       currently playing audio or video.

  c) Elapsed Time Information:
     - Press "C" to retrieve and announce the elapsed playback time of
       the current media.

  d) Full Screen Bug Fix:
     - In previous versions, pressing the Enter key would activate full
       screen mode for both audio and video streams. This was an unintended
       behavior, as full screen mode is not applicable to audio-only
       streams. This issue has been corrected; full screen mode is now
       available only for video streams.


================================================================================
BUG FIXES
================================================================================

  - Resolved media playback issues that caused interruptions and errors
    during audio and video streaming.
  - Fixed UI freezing issues that caused the application to become
    unresponsive during certain operations.
  - Addressed downloading errors that prevented successful file saves
    under specific conditions.


================================================================================
ADDITIONAL IMPROVEMENTS
================================================================================

  - Dynamic Search Results Window Title:
    After performing a search, the search results window title now reflects
    the query that was entered. For example, searching for "English grammar
    lesson" will set the window title to:
    "English grammar lesson - YouTube Search"
    This enhancement improves navigation and context awareness when working
    with multiple windows.

  - Search Results Playback:
    In the search results window, double-clicking or selecting a video in
    the results list will begin video playback. To play the content as
    audio only, press CTRL+ENTER or click the "Play as Audio" button.


================================================================================
CLOSING NOTES
================================================================================

